{"tid":1668660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[溫馨提示] 因為條戇鳩三跑香港市民要俾多180蚊稅","createTime":"2019-10-22T06:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T06:18:49.000Z","uid":38548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"811c8735da7a37e3dce5f8708d23adcce09ff8a4","tid":1668660,"uid":38548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:12:56.000Z","msg":"而家傳政府資助120蚊市民外遊<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚識計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />施捨呀？"},{"pid":"1d1a77aeac6afc6addcf735c55b05b8eb6adff97","tid":1668660,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"b43127022d03a7202e623dd7e4f5869f218e1204","tid":1668660,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:17:17.000Z","msg":"120 蚊咋？"},{"pid":"11f1071e032da0092ea19e66fd3e5a4844a970c3","tid":1668660,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,